    "summary": "In this transcript, a user describes classic symptoms of hypoglycemia (shaking, sweating, confusion) following exercise and proposes taking insulin to \"balance\" themselves. The assistant repeatedly and correctly identifies these as signs of low blood sugar and strongly advises against taking insulin, instead recommending fast-acting carbohydrates and emergency medical attention.",
